      </item>
    
      <item>
        <title>Xcode git 忽略user interface state文件</title>
        <description>&lt;ol&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;退出xcdoe， 打开终端（Terminal），进入到你的项目目录下&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;在终端键入  git rm –cached [YourProjectName].xcodeproj/project.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/[YourUsername].xcuserdatad/UserInterfaceState.xcuserstate&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;在终端键入  git commit -m ‘Removed file that shouldn’t be tracked’&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;在你的项目目录下新建.gitignore文件，加入如下几行&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;*.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;xcuserstate&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;project&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;xcworkspace&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;xcuserdata&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;UserInterfaceState&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;xcuserstate&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;project&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;xcworkspace&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;xcuserdata&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;UserInterface&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;xcuserstate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;重新打开Xcode commit, push。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
        <pubDate>Sun, 06 Sep 2015 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
        <link>kikidesign.github.io/ios/git/2015/09/06/user-interface-state.html</link>
        <guid isPermaLink="true">kikidesign.github.io/ios/git/2015/09/06/user-interface-state.html</guid>
        
        
        <category>ios</category>
        
        <category>git</category>
        
      </item>
    
      <item>
        <title>no visible @interface for XXX declares the selector YYY</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;异常信息：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;no&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;visible&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;vi&quot;&gt;@interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;XXX&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;declares&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;selector&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;YYY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;一般而言，发生异常的代码行，是因为没有在.h文件interface接口中申明方法。&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
        <pubDate>Wed, 02 Sep 2015 22:57:00 +0800</pubDate>
